      "text": "8 B counter + 56 B pad = 64\nB<br>STILL only half a 128-B line.\n<br>Production fix: pad to 120\nB<br>or use\nruntime/internal/sys.CacheLinePad",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "S9-wmGIMdc15KTgC2zK8n",
      "originalText": "8 B counter + 56 B pad = 64 B<br>STILL only half a 128-B line.<br>Production fix: pad to 120 B<br>or use runtime/internal/sys.CacheLinePad",
