      "versionNonce": 699320593,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778165443149,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Note[Sarama spawns ConsumeClaim<br/>**once per\nassigned partition**.<br/>So 12 goroutines run · not 4.\n<br/>time.Sleep(4ms) fires from 12 of them.<br/>\n<br/>Throughput ≈ 1000ms/6ms × 12 ≈ 2 000\nmsg/s<br/>matches observed 1 938 msg/s]:::n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Note[Sarama spawns ConsumeClaim<br/>**once per assigned partition**.<br/>So 12 goroutines run · not 4.<br/>time.Sleep(4ms) fires from 12 of them.<br/><br/>Throughput ≈ 1000ms/6ms × 12 ≈ 2 000 msg/s<br/>matches observed 1 938 msg/s]:::n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
